00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,080
Right.
对。

175
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:24,120
So it would be correct to say, I'm going to write a business plan or I have to write a
所以正确说法是“我要写一份商业计划”或“我必须写一份商业计划”。

176
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,440
business plan.
商业计划。

177
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:30,440
But if you use this phrase, I'm going to write up a business plan, it's more fluent, right?
但如果你用这个短语“我要起草一份商业计划”，会更流利，对吧？

178
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,440
It's just more native-like.
更像母语者说的。

179
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,440
Exactly.
没错。

180
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,440
All right.
好的。

181
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:36,720
And our next phrase is a return on investment.
我们的下一个短语是“投资回报”。

182
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,720
Okay.
好的。

183
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,760
So early we talked about investors.
之前我们谈到了投资者。

