00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:03,920
the phone and get food delivered to your house.
送到你家。

217
00:10:03,920 --> 00:10:04,920
Right.
对。

218
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:08,880
So you can change here, you can say save myself, save yourself, save his self.
所以这里可以变化，你可以说“省得我自己麻烦”、“省得你自己麻烦”、“省得他自己麻烦”。

219
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:10,440
So you change that pronoun.
所以你要改变那个代词。

220
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,440
The pronoun.
代词。

221
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,440
Exactly.
没错。

222
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:15,840
So you can save yourself the hassle or I'm just going to save myself the hassle.
所以你可以说“省得你自己麻烦”或“我就省得自己麻烦了”。

223
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,840
Okay.
好的。

224
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,880
