天哪，就这些吗？

255
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,000
Almost.
差不多。

256
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:51,320
The most important piece of information for your investors will be the financial analysis.
对投资者来说，最重要的信息将是财务分析。

257
